geneity that could contribute to the seismic signature of the\nLAB.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Aug 2016 16:27:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Feb 2017 22:34:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-15"}
