ditions through measuring the asymmetry. Mutual confirmation between\nanalytical model and numerical simulations is found in terms of the cratering\ndistribution and its variation with $a_{\\rm{M}}$. Estimates of $A_1$ for crater\ndensity distributions generated by the MBAs and the NEOs are 0.101--0.159 and\n0.117, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Aug 2016 17:25:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-12"}
