e validity of collisional-MHD description of\nturbulence properties in the collisionless IGM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 13 Aug 2016 02:15:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 2 Oct 2016 17:15:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-14"}
